20finally%20pinpointed%2011%20styling%20products%20that%20are%20guaranteed%20to%20give%20me%20a%20good%20wash%20and%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20moisturizing%20curl%20creams%20to%20curl-defining%20mousse%2C%20here%20are%20the%20styling%20products%20that%20completely%20transformed%20my%20hair%20care%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20curl%20routine%20at%20a%20glance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20wash%20days%20(1-2%20a%20week)%2C%20wash%20hair%20with%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20or%20co-wash.%20Apply%20a%20deep%20conditioner%20for%205-30%20minutes%20to%20lock%20in%20extra%20moisture.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20still%20wet%2C%20add%20curl%20cream%2C%20hard%20hold%20gel%2C%20or%20mousse%2C%20using%20a%20detangling%20brush%20or%20wide-tooth%20comb%20to%20spread%20the%20product%20evenly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScrunch%20out%20extra%20water%20with%20a%20cotton%20T-shirt%20and%20let%20air%20dry%20for%2010-20%20minutes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDry%20using%20a%20diffuser%20and%20heat%20protectant.%20Seal%20with%20anti-frizz%20oil.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECreams%20that%20keep%20my%20curls%20soft%20and%20defined%3Cp%3EMost%20wash%20days%2C%20I%20combine%20a%20curl%20cream%20for%20moisture%20and%20set%20it%20with%20a%20hard%20gel.%20My%20hair%20has%20medium%20density%20and%20low%20porosity%20%E2%80%94%20it%20holds%20onto%20water%20for%20a%20long%20time%20but%20takes%20forever%20to%20actually%20soak%20it%20up%20in%20the%20shower.%20That%20means%20I%20have%20to%20be%20intentional%20about%20locking%20in%20moisture%20and%20using%20products%20that%20don't%20just%20sit%20on%20top.%20These%20three%20creams%20are%20my%20go-to%20for%20keeping%20my%20curls%20nourished%20and%20defined%20throughout%20New%20York%20City's%20many%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGels%20that%20lock%20everything%20in%3Cp%3ECreams%20lay%20the%20foundation%2C%20but%20gels%20are%20what%20seal%20the%20deal.%20I'm%20picky%20with%20gels%20%E2%80%94%20I%20want%20a%20strong%20hol