20Dehradun%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20to%20the%20mountains%20ignited%20a%20passion%20that%20never%20left%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20escape%20into%20forests%20and%20mountains%20whenever%20I%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijay%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20he%20graduated%20in%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20from%20Dev%20Bhoomi%20Uttarakhand%20University%20and%20began%20working%20with%20HCL%20in%20Hyderabad.%20However%2C%20adjusting%20to%20life%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20proved%20tough.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20manage%20food%20and%20the%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20nature%20became%20his%20solace%2C%20and%20weekends%20offered%20him%20the%20perfect%20escape%20into%20the%20wilderness.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20interested%20in%20wildlife%20photography%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I%20used%20to%20explore%20nearby%20forests.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20found%20solace%20in%20trekking%20and%20nature%20wherever%20he%20went.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162813.520-1744801735-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-420858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVijay%20found%20solace%20in%20trekking%20and%20nature%20wherever%20he%20went.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20grow%20professionally%2C%20Vijay%20took%20the%20MAT%20(Management%20Aptitude%20Test)%20and%20pursued%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20international%20business%20from%20Chandigarh%20University.%20During%20his%20final%20year%2C%20he%20was%20working%20with%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20in%20Pune%2C%20where%20he%20gained%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20how%20businesses%20operated.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20those%20client%20conversations%2C%20I%20learned%20about%20business%20strategies%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20doing%20well%20in%20his%20banking%20role%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20his%20heart%20remained%20in%20the%20mountains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20continued%20hiking%20and%20trekking%20with%20my%20friends%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20who%20refused%20to%20let%20go%20of%20his%20connection%20with%20the%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Vijay%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20trekking%20for%20leisure.%20He%20was%20planning%20something%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20leap%20at%2023%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdvenThrill%20is%20an%20outdoor%20adventure%20programme%20that%20organises%20treks%20for%20college%20students%2C%20working%20professionals%20or%20anyone%20interested%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20learning-based%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijay%20explains.%20The%20vision%20for%20AdvenThrill%20had%20been%20years%20in%20the%20making%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%20the%20time%20he%20quit%20his%20job%2C%20he%20knew%20exactly%20how%20it%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361918%2Fadventure-map-of-india-hot-air-balloon-trekking-skiing-caving-safari-rappelling-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarting%20an%20adventure%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20impulsive%20decision.%20It%20was%20something%20Vijay%20had%20already%20mapped%20out%20%E2%80%94%20a%20well-calculated%20risk%2C%20backed%20by%20experience%20and%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20for%20the%20mountains.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20I%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20I%20had%20already%20planned%20what%20the%20company%20would%20be%20and%20how%20it%20would%20function%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20his%20IT%20friends%2C%20Vijay%20created%20a%20website%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20for%20AdvenThrill%2C%20so%20that%20the%20first%20wheel%20%E2%80%94%20trek%20booking%20%E2%80%94%20could%20start%20chugging.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20hired%20a%20few%20management%20interns%20to%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20running%20of%20the%20company.%20But%20I%20was%20handling%2080%25%20of%20the%20work%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20had%20a%20concrete%20plan%20before%20establishing%20his%20adventure%20company.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-16T162953.471-1744801205-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the