used%20to%20eat%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20toughest%20challenges%20was%20working%20with%20millet%20milk%2C%20which%2C%20unlike%20regular%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20contains%20tiny%20dust%20particles.%20%E2%80%9CFiltering%20out%20these%20particles%20without%20losing%20the%20nutritional%20value%20was%20a%20major%20hurdle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20His%20engineering%20skills%20became%20indispensable%20as%20he%20designed%20and%20built%20a%20specialised%20machine%20to%20filter%20the%20millet%20milk%20effectively%2C%20producing%20a%20smooth%20and%20nutrient-rich%20base%20for%20the%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20process%20had%20to%20be%20invented%20from%20scratch%20as%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20market%20to%20filter%20millet%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20First%2C%20the%20naturally%20grown%20millets%20are%20sourced%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%20and%20farmer%20producer%20organisations.%20These%20grains%20are%20carefully%20washed%20and%20dried%20to%20remove%20dust.%20The%20cleaned%20millets%20are%20then%20milled%20and%20filtered%20to%20extract%20the%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20artificial%20flavours%3A%20Just%20real%20fruit%2C%20real%20grain%2C%20and%20real%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20millet%20milk%20is%20prepared%2C%20it%20is%20mixed%20with%20a%20natural%20stabiliser%2C%20developed%20in-house%2C%20and%20a%20modest%20amount%20of%20sugar%2C%20usually%20between%20five%20and%2012%20percent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruit%20used.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20steer%20clear%20of%20artificial%20colours%20or%20flavours.%20Every%20taste%20comes%20directly%20from%20real%20fruit%20pulp%20and%20nuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20making%20of%20millet%20ice%20cream%20is%20a%20meticulous%20and%20multi-step%20process.%20After%20mixing%20the%20millet%20milk%2C%20stabiliser%2C%20and%20sugar%20in%20a%20large%20tank%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20gently%20heated%20and%20boiled%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20is%20safe%20and%20properly%20combined.%20Next%2C%20it%20undergoes%20homogenisation%20to%20break%20down%20fat%20molecules%20for%20a%20creamy%20texture%2C%20followed%20by%20pasteurisation%20to%20kill%20any%20harmful%20bacteria.%20The%20mixture%20is%20then%20aged%20for%20approximately%20eight%20hours%2C%20which%20helps%20develop%20the%20right%20consistency%20and%20flavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20consists%20of%20eight%20permanent%20employees%20who%20work%20in%20the%20factory%20daily%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-02T163702.822_11zon-1751454456-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-460310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20consists%20of%20eight%20pe