cision.%20They%20left%20their%20stable%20IT%20careers%20behind%20and%20returned%20to%20Guntur%2C%20investing%20their%20savings%20of%20Rs%2017%20lakh%20into%20a%20new%20venture%2C%20%E2%80%98Sreshte%E2%80%99.%20The%20name%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20Sanskrit%20word%20meaning%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cexcellent%E2%80%9D%2C%20perfectly%20encapsulated%20their%20vision%2C%20to%20offer%20only%20the%20finest%20organic%20products%2C%20grounded%20in%20their%20commitment%20to%20health%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202017%2C%20Kotinaga%20Manikanta%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Durga%20Pavani%20returned%20to%20Guntur%20to%20establish%20Sreshte%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F20220308_181044-1_11zon-1733380735-200x150.jpg%20200w